<body><main class="wrap"><header class="hero"><div><div class="eyebrow">BEYOND TATTOO · CREATIVE STUDIO</div><h1>High-end stencil generator</h1><p>Describe an original concept, generate professional transfer-ready artwork with OpenAI, review it, then publish it directly to the Beyond Tattoo library.</p></div><span class="badge">GPT Image 2 · High quality</span></header><section class="grid"><article class="card"><div class="field"><label for="idea">Ask for a stencil</label><textarea id="idea" placeholder="Example: A celestial lion with a crescent halo, sacred geometry and flowing botanical accents. Strong central silhouette with open negative space."></textarea><small>Describe an original concept rather than requesting an exact copy of another artist.</small></div><div class="row"><div class="field"><label for="style">Style</label><select id="style"><option>Fine-line blackwork</option><option>Neo-traditional linework</option><option>Geometric ornamental</option><option>Engraving realism</option><option>Japanese-inspired flow</option><option>Minimalist single-line</option></select></div><div class="field"><label for="placement">Placement</label><select id="placement"><option>Outer forearm</option><option>Upper arm</option><option>Calf</option><option>Thigh</option><option>Back panel</option><option>Sternum</option></select></div></div><div class="field"><label for="title">Library title</label><input id="title" maxlength="100" placeholder="Celestial Lion"></div><div class="field"><label for="collection">Collection</label><select id="collection"><option>Beyond Divine Collection</option><option>Beyond Ancient Collection</option><option>Beyond Dark Collection</option><option>Beyond Japanese Collection</option></select></div><div class="actions"><button class="btn" id="generate">✦ Generate high-end stencil</button><button class="btn secondary" id="clear" type="button">Clear preview</button></div><p class="status" id="status" aria-live="polite"></p><div class="publish" id=